msgid ""
"The :c:type:`TSVConn` the plugin receives as the result of successful "
"operates identically to one created through :c:type:`TSNetConnect`. Aside"
" from allowing the plugin to set the client ip and port for logging, the "
"functionality of :c:func:`TSHttpConnect` is identical to connecting to "
"localhost on the proxy port with :c:func:`TSNetConnect`. "
":c:func:`TSHttpConnect` is more efficient than :c:func:`TSNetConnect` to "
"localhost since it avoids the overhead of passing the data through the "
"operating system."
msgstr ""

